title: FOOGO Green 200pcs Disposable Wooden Forks and Knives Set, FSC® Certified, 100x Forks, 100x Knives, 16cm Wooden, Biodegradable, Eco Friendly, Bamboo Cutlery Set, Party
features: PREMIUM QUALITY and STURDY – Made from high quality birch wood, our disposable wooden cutlery set is sturdy and a perfect eco-friendly alternative to disposable plastic cutlery.
STRONG FORKS and SHARP KNIVES – Suitable for any type of food. Easy to cut through meat making it ideal for all kinds of parties.

ECO-FRIENDLY – Made from sustainable sources, we have taken every care possible to ensure there is no plastic used in the product packaging. FOOGO Green wooden cutlery is a perfect alternative for disposable plastic cutlery or bamboo cutlery.
BIODEGRADABLE and COMPOSTABLE – when used, can go straight into compost bin. Easy and safe disposal into fire pits during camping trips and barbecues.
GREAT FOR PARTIES – Ideal for birthday parties, weddings, camps, barbecue, catering and corporate events. Also available disposable wooden spoons, disposable bowls, disposable plates, etc.

One-stop-shop for ECO PARTY SUPPLIES - Our range of products includes disposable palm leaf plates, disposable wooden cutlery sets, eco-friendly napkins, biodegradable straws, disposable bowls, serving trays and more.

A greener alternative. Old challenge. New solution. We believe that convenience shouldn't be at the cost of the planet. Decades of single-use plastic usage is having an adverse impact on the planet and this is our solution. FOOGO Green wooden cutlery is made from birch wood, a fast growing tree and a fairly sustainable source of wood. Be good. Do good. We are FSC certified . This is our commitment to ensuring healthy, resilient forests for all. We are Carbon Neutral . We offset all carbon emissions right from manufacturing, all the way to delivery to customers. Gift from nature. Designed for convenience. FOOGO Green wooden cutlery is designed with convenience in mind. Deep spoons, strong forks and sharp knives - they are a sensible option for a variety of foods. When used they can be disposed off along with food waste or even burnt in campfires and barbecues. All occasions. Be it a wedding, corporate event or a backyard barbecue, our eco-conscious tableware is a sensible option. They are perfect for zero waste parties, picnics, camping and outside events where it may not be possible to wash-up afterwards.
